snippet.title: Madame Fay’s New Fortunes
snippet.description:
With the release of Destination Arcterra, Madame Fay has all new fortunes! Get a chance at three random prizes with the use of Fortune Coins—from cosmetics, to boosts, to mounts—and may Madame Fay’s fortunes smile upon you.

You can find more information about WildStar at: http://www.WildStar-Online.com/ 

Like us on Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/WildStarOnline 
Follow us on Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/WildStar
